{"tid":2310129,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"年輕人受啟蒙參政 籲港人「自己抗爭」","createTime":"2020-12-03T04:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T04:59:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0df13cf00b9167fce37f76f0524580522da2933a","tid":2310129,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:47:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201203/ZO3DW6TXDZETBFOAYLZLZCL7YQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201203%2FZO3DW6TXDZETBFOAYLZLZCL7YQ%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPeUDsY8FkShsNjUL6uXjEIs%3D&h=e22065f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201203%2FZO3DW6TXDZETBFOAYLZLZCL7YQ%2F&h=5c8d736f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201203/ZO3DW6TXDZETBFOAYLZLZCL7YQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n年輕人受啟蒙參政 籲港人「自己抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GKsFWIiSfbeKsImEI48RQWAxAjA=/1200x919/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MY6UMZ74TBFEDGSTIHGRQNPGOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGKsFWIiSfbeKsImEI48RQWAxAjA%3D%2F1200x919%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMY6UMZ74TBFEDGSTIHGRQNPGOU.jpg&h=bb041e5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄒家成、王百羽及周炫瑋均受學民啟蒙而投身社運及參政。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】2012年國民教育科壓境，學民思潮一眾中學生首次以領袖之姿走到鎂光燈前；2014年中央就選舉辦法「落三閘」，學民與學聯再次登上「大台」反抗。站在台上的學生領袖如今接連面對牢獄之苦，當年坐在台下仰望，受啟蒙矢志投身社運的80、90後少年人為數不少，當中包括三個已參政的年輕人，即鄒家成、王百羽及周炫瑋。其中鄒家成對三人被判入獄感痛心，籲港人學習「自己抗爭」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盼眾人從容面對苦難<br />\n<br />\n鄒家成在周庭被捕當晚傳了一張舊照給黃之鋒打氣，照片內的鄒穿着白色T恤，胸前和手上別着黃絲帶，還戴着一隻鮮紅色電子錶，坐在人群中高舉橙色的「開閘」文宣。那是2014年9.26罷課集會當日被傳媒拍下的相片，那年他正讀中六。當晚眾人在黃之鋒一聲號召下衝入公民廣場，「當時嚟講已經係相對激進&hellip;&hellip;覺得大家好團結、都幾亢奮！」<br />\n<br />\n訪問前一日，鄒到荔枝角收押所探望黃之鋒。鄒稱二人因12港人事件多了交集。遙想當年，他感激學民思潮擔當引領者角色，將當時零散的中學生罷課行動聚焦，「中學生&hellip;&hellip;大家都奀嫋鬼命咁，原來成班集結埋一齊係可以咁樣面對警察㗎喎」。他稱雨傘運動是他的政治啟蒙，至2016年反釋法，他自言已走得更前。今年年中，他以本土派定位參加民主派初選並出線；12港人被扣押後，鄒家成一直協助家屬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/U5IE5-IbNU93QnhxW7-BBPx8x1g=/1773x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3HLEIVKRNBAHBF4R35HQ5BPP34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FU5IE5-IbNU93QnhxW7-BBPx8x1g%3D%2F1773x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3HLEIVKRNBAHBF4R35HQ5BPP34.jpg&h=c16487e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄒家成在周庭被捕當晚傳了一張舊照給黃之鋒打氣，是2014年9.26罷課集會他被傳媒拍下的相片。鄒家成fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n大埔區議員周炫瑋在反國教那年大學畢業，相比當時學民思潮15、16歲的成員，他已屬較年長參與者。<span class=\"orange\">他記得黃之鋒等人曾在公民廣場一角換校服準備上學，印象深刻，「都幾感動&hellip;&hellip;覺得連中學生都企到咁前，我哋都唔能夠缺席」</span>，令他更堅定抗爭的決心。<br />\n<br />\n王百羽於2019年區選中，在天水圍天恒選區成功挑戰建制派。他稱反國教前，連六四集會也不常出席，2012年反國教事件後，始關注社會議題。學民三子今次被判囚，王籲眾人「從容、堅強」面對苦難，勿忘初心。<br />\n<br />\n他們不約而同稱，即使學民三人暫時失去自由身，外面的人也不會放棄抗爭，「或者香港人要學習、嘗試喺無政治人物嘅協助下，自己抗爭」。"},{"pid":"387620bd7ca74bd13cb622d7d6fb354fb0928e99","tid":2310129,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf266f2b471fa01d67599d29c1aa5a395c9f7d7","tid":2310129,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:59:52.000Z","msg":"想當年天琦都係受雨革啟蒙先參與政治"}]}